Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the 100 million\NBerries we had in here go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I gave it to them to buy meat\Nand booze and stuff for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we got a good deal with the ship,\Nso there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami! I'm gonna go out and have fun,\Nso give me some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,@#$%&!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Girl in Search of Her Yagara!\NGreat Search in the City of Water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aobire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice of you, Chopper. Thanks for\Ntreating me to this water-water candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! After all,\Nshe did give me 10,000 Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the rest of the money\Nto buy medical books.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Our town's hero's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Yo! Party King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had fun yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you!\N--Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Nami just got done scolding you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,1)}"Missing Yagara"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the way you ate\Nwas really something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really admiring, Party King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we pick up where we\Nleft off yesterday at my place today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If that's the case, come to my place!\N--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's coming to my place first!\N--If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, my place!\N--My place!\N--he's the pirate who saved Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My place!\N--My place!\N--If it's him, maybe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi! You left without having breakfast again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should give up on finding Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll have him eat at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We'll have a party at my place first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No! He'll come to my place!\N--Your place is tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family's Yagara went missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me find him... I mean, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Abi, the photographer's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's still looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three days since the Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad, but he's probably gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was already over 100 years old.\NThat big wave was too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump him with the\Nstupid Yagara you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big wave wouldn't be\Nenough to take out our Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--Now, now... Calm down, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, he might have\Nsurvived the Aqua Laguna,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he hasn't been back for\Nthree days now, so he, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's right. You shouldn't\Ndrag Straw Hat into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Water Seven,\Ntoo, so you should know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the story about Yagaras seeking out\Ntheir "final nesting village"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has seen that place,\Nso I'm not gonna believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire appeared in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Straw Hat! You pirates\Nlove treasure, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the money I have!\NIf you find him, I'll give it all to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You'll give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's if you find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't bother, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you, by any chance, come to step\Ninto their final nesting village...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite get it, but it is true\Nthat pirates can't just pass up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,treasure that's right in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That treasure of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Abi! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper, our ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The little raccoon dog spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a little raccoon dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what am I supposed to find again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening?!\NAobire! My family's Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know it's him by the blue fin on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fin is blue, so his name is Aobire, huh?\NI like it. It's easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are we starting our search here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? This is the best place to\Nlook out over the city, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to town already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! I'm here!\NI'm right here! Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice! It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Nami! Robin!\N--Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. If we ask Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Yagara with a blue fin on his head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojos Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Robin, we now know that\Nhe isn't on the shipbuilding island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The good news is that it saved us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Abi. Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the final nesting village that\Nthe townspeople were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that when Yagaras realize\Ntheir lives are about to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they leave their groups or their owners\Nand go to a certain place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the final nesting village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--But?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if humans see this final nesting village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they see it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll also be taken to the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a superstition!\NThere's no need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, captain! Do you need\Na sniper for your pirate group?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This humble, flattering plan isn't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I got a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof! I'm not gonna let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check the backstreets, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone who heard Aobire's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So on the night of the Aqua Laguna,\Nyou heard someone around here say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm coming to rescue you, so hang in there"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it was definitely\NGrandpa Aobire's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Abi!\N--Yeah! Thank you, little guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible that you\Nunderstand the Yagara's language!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it! I'm not a "little guy," you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know that, let's thoroughly\Nsearch this area, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking all over for him, and yet, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Watch out! Not that direction, Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, is it true that Aobire can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's an old Yagara who\Nturned 100 a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that there's no chance\Nthat his sight will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire has been serving our\Nfamily very well for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can no longer deny\Nthe decline in his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should start preparing ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't know how\Nbest to explain it to Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Aobire's coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take him to the evacuation facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do this every year. You should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our house is in the center of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'll be swallowed\Nby the Aqua Laguna, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he really was\Nswallowed by the Aqua Laguna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fish would drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked you to help him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can cry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! We know the\Narea we should be searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Aobire's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it come from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an entrance to the\Nunderground waterways!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Aobire!\N--Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where are you?!\N--Aobire!\N--Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go any farther on the Yagara like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water ahead of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's try moving ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here and wait for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? There's a town\Nunderneath the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me once that they built\Nnew buildings above the old ones
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kept doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Abi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see him soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Little guy! Are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Abi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Aobire is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same place that I saw in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... this is the final nesting village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right! The final\Nnesting village is a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like Aobire is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a story created to\Nexplain mysteries about the Yagaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! So you were there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire! Come here! Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, "I'm sorry, Abi."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?!\NI wanted to see you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not mad about\Nyour sudden disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! Let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now I can feel at ease."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks for everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you to the final nesting village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aobire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:20:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--A Yagara's voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heartbeat is weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I think he'll be able to pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the scarf kept him\Nwarm and helped him survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the scarf that I gave to Aobire...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll rescue you now, so hang in there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aobire tried to save him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he appeared in my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I couldn't keep my promise, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you two,\NI was able to see Aobire again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was able to grant his last wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to save this baby Yagara, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:22:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll need lots of food in\Norder to get strong, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think that place\Nwas the final nesting village?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the world is full of mysteries\Nthat we know nothing about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, everyone!\NWe're gonna go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. I have nothing to do\Nwith you guys! Why do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, carry the younger ones on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can carry two babies on my back...\NHey, that's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mothers Are Strong!\NZoro's Hectic Household Chores!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
